{"tid":2479183,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】本田小狼與我","createTime":"2021-04-07T15:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T18:05:33.000Z","uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b753be6b02c37a9540f9b2536c196cbc8d00073b","tid":2479183,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQFpx7UVM8VsMT5t965CmxCxWrcPoArHsDJjcQVm4s7WN?filename=DkJYu3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkJYu3G.jpg&h=19b26cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由 トネ・コーケン所著、博繪製插圖的輕小說《本田小狼與我》，宣布將推出電視動畫，2021年4月7日開播。<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介：<br />\n<br />\n小熊是一名就讀山梨縣高中的女孩子。舉目無親，也沒有朋友和興趣，日子一無所有的她，獲得了一輛中古的 Super Cub。初次騎機車上學、沒油、繞路而行──光是這樣的小事，就令她有種稍稍進行了一場冒險的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n對些微變化感到滿意的小熊，同學禮子找她攀談：「我也是騎機車上學。妳要看嗎？」一輛本田小狼讓她的世界綻放了小小的光輝。這便是孤苦伶仃的女孩子和世上最優秀的機車之間，編織而成的一段日常與友情的故事。<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NbWU6B0qjMY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNbWU6B0qjMY&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=77f7844e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NbWU6B0qjMY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0Dzuu9exl2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0Dzuu9exl2s&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=fed7df8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0Dzuu9exl2s</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>STAFF</strong><br />\n原作：トネ・コーケン<br />\n插圖：博<br />\n監督：藤井俊郎<br />\n系列構成、脚本：根元歳三<br />\n角色設定：今西亨<br />\n色彩設計：大西峰代<br />\n美術設定：多田周平<br />\n美術監督：須江信人<br />\n撮影監督：浅川茂輝<br />\n背景：草薙<br />\n編集：齋藤朱里<br />\n協力・監修：本田技研工業株式会社<br />\n音楽：石川智久・ZAQ<br />\n制作：スタジオ KAI<br />\n製作：ベアモータース<br />\n<br />\n<strong>CAST</strong><br />\n小熊：夜道雪<br />\n禮子：七瀨彩夏<br />\n惠庭椎：日岡夏美<br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://supercub-anime.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupercub-anime.com&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=8e738b96\" target=\"_blank\">https://supercub-anime.com</a>"},{"pid":"1ea5798493834e12a5d8e336478b791e51aa0918","tid":2479183,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"有大水喉應該幾dum本，木棉花有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fff06ecada4d8344a26cdbd50db34aea589075","tid":2479183,"uid":68058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"今季食糧"},{"pid":"65c8ec63e8032aa7923adc67d6c8132c62249817","tid":2479183,"uid":62578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"依套唔錯<br />\n<br />\n今集話咁快就睇完<br />\n<br />\n希望之後保持倒"},{"pid":"4f0700c3b78bc877094550d367692b188fddb79d","tid":2479183,"uid":28916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"睇得出幾有米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6b719cde567afd89dd6dc180044478a1992b34","tid":2479183,"uid":28916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"節奏慢到，但又覺得幾治癒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主角一開到車成個畫面顏色都變曬  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1c670afe61387ecb7475ba69080fdef0924c91","tid":2479183,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"幾靚 有療癒feel 唔知啲色係咪特燈整有啲怪 同埋女主角孤兒嚟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2d76eae3a2266df14064e17fc857eecdd890fb","tid":2479183,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"有人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今季難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fda0954642a8bd0f58ec68190a270f6a9ab5d82","tid":2479